query:
SELECT 
                    user_id as "user_id: QsUserId", 
                    encrypted_push_token as "encrypted_push_token: EncryptedPushToken", 
                    owner_public_key, 
                    owner_signature_key, 
                    ratchet, 
                    activity_time as "activity_time: TimeStamp"
                FROM 
                    qs_client_records 
                WHERE 
                    client_id = $1
